<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:14_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:14_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:14_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:14_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A commit is only for binaries; a push is only for source code</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:14_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:14_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:14_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:14_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They are identical operations with different names</div></div> </div>
