<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:20_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:20_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:20_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which statement is most accurate about using timestamps vs checksums as file signatures in build systems?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 20</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:20_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:20_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:20_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:20_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Using checksums makes it impossible to rebuild older versions</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:20_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:20_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:20_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:20_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Checksums cannot detect a one-character change in source code</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:20_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:20_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:20_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:20_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Checksums reflect content changes directly, while timestamps reflect modification times and can be less robust for parallel version builds</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:20_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:20_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:20_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:20_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Timestamps change only when the file content changes, never for other reasons</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><span class="filter_mathjaxloader_equation"><p>Checksums (e.g., <span class="nolink"><mjx-container class="MathJax CtxtMenu_Attached_0" jax="CHTML" tabindex="0" ctxtmenu_counter="0" style="font-size: 120.2%; position: relative;"><mjx-math class="MJX-TEX" aria-hidden="true"><mjx-mi class="mjx-i"><mjx-c class="mjx-c210E TEX-I"></mjx-c></mjx-mi><mjx-mo class="mjx-n"><mjx-c class="mjx-c28"></mjx-c></mjx-mo><mjx-mtext class="mjx-n"><mjx-c class="mjx-c73"></mjx-c><mjx-c class="mjx-c6F"></mjx-c><mjx-c class="mjx-c75"></mjx-c><mjx-c class="mjx-c72"></mjx-c><mjx-c class="mjx-c63"></mjx-c><mjx-c class="mjx-c65"></mjx-c></mjx-mtext><mjx-mo class="mjx-n"><mjx-c class="mjx-c29"></mjx-c></mjx-mo></mjx-math><mjx-assistive-mml unselectable="on" display="inline"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mtext>source</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></mjx-assistive-mml></mjx-container></span>) change with any content change and can support parallel builds more robustly than timestamps alone.</p></span></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Checksums reflect content changes directly, while timestamps reflect modification times and can be less robust for parallel version builds</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-21" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">21</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_138"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:21_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=530915&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11629&amp;slot=21&amp;checksum=be6fb81769afc6ef672b04431a7230a9&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
