</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: The framework controls the flow and calls application-specific code via events and callbacks.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-40" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">40</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_252"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:40_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=530934&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11507&amp;slot=40&amp;checksum=c28b905a27be27db1348bf9eda0d709b&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
