</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Common strategies include reducing likelihood (avoidance), reducing impact (minimization), and preparing actions if the risk occurs (contingency plans).</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Avoidance, minimization, contingency plans</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-52" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">52</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_324"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:52_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=530946&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11593&amp;slot=52&amp;checksum=ff75466f5a0ecd3cdb4496244011ae62&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
