</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>'What-if' questions help teams imagine plausible disruptions and develop prepared responses.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: To explore scenarios so avoidance and contingency actions can be prepared in advance</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-53" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">53</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_330"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:53_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=530947&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11594&amp;slot=53&amp;checksum=69dde6386afebcf2aaf61732eace60e4&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
