<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:59_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:59_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:59_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:59_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">It guarantees the highest productivity because everyone thinks the same way</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Homogeneous motivation profiles can create imbalance (e.g., too much individual focus or too much chatting). Balanced teams tend to function better.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: It can amplify a single weakness (e.g., everyone wants to lead, or too much discussion and not enough execution)</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-60" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">60</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_372"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:60_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=530954&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11601&amp;slot=60&amp;checksum=390aed2acb98a3f6dcb24af94fa56662&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
