<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:65_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:65_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:65_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:65_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">The leader assigns every task unilaterally without discussion</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Informal groups often decide by consensus; the leader interfaces externally but tasks are discussed and allocated based on ability and experience.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: The team discusses work collectively and allocates tasks based on ability and experience, with the leader serving as an external interface</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-66" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">66</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_408"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:66_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=530960&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11607&amp;slot=66&amp;checksum=dade8a4bc882df6fda72fd3fc313245c&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
