<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:80_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:80_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:80_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which statement best describes <b>security engineering</b> in software development?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 80</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:80_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:80_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:80_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:80_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">It is primarily about maximizing performance by removing authentication checks.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:80_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:80_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:80_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:80_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">It applies tools, techniques, and methods to help systems resist malicious attacks that could damage the system or its data.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:80_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:80_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:80_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:80_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">It focuses exclusively on making systems user-friendly, even if that weakens protection.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:80_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:80_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:80_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:80_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">It only concerns physical security such as locks and surveillance cameras.</div></div> </div>
