<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:92_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:92_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:92_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which option best distinguishes <b>application security</b> from <b>infrastructure security</b>?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 92</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:92_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:92_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:92_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:92_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Application security is about physical access; infrastructure security is about cryptography only.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:92_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:92_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:92_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:92_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Application security only concerns firewalls; infrastructure security only concerns code reviews.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:92_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:92_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:92_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:92_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They are identical terms and used interchangeably in engineering practice.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:92_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:92_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:92_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:92_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Application security is primarily a software engineering/design problem; infrastructure security is primarily a systems configuration/management problem.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Application security focuses on software design/implementation resisting attacks, while infrastructure security focuses on configuration and management of shared systems and networks.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Application security is primarily a software engineering/design problem; infrastructure security is primarily a systems configuration/management problem.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-93" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">93</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_570"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:93_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=530987&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11548&amp;slot=93&amp;checksum=4b0024ad9128a6e607dc3c907c969cee&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
