<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:95_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:95_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:95_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Why is <b>operational security</b> often described as primarily a human and social issue?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 95</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:95_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:95_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:95_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:95_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because users may take convenient but insecure actions, creating a trade-off between security and getting work done effectively.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:95_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:95_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:95_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:95_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because operational security is unrelated to policy and procedures.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:95_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:95_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:95_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:95_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because operational security only involves selecting a programming language.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:95_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:95_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:95_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:95_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because operational security can be solved completely by adding more encryption.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Operational security focuses on preventing insecure user behavior (e.g., sharing passwords, leaving sessions open) and balancing security with effectiveness.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Because users may take convenient but insecure actions, creating a trade-off between security and getting work done effectively.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-96" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">96</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_588"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:96_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=530990&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11549&amp;slot=96&amp;checksum=04a0ebce4a1ce13660fce52ff21ef076&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
