<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:96_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:96_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:96_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:96_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A requirement that is always written explicitly in the contract.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:96_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:96_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:96_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:96_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A system-level characteristic that arises from interactions among components and may only be evaluated after integration.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:96_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:96_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:96_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:96_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A feature that exists only in software, never in hardware systems.</div></div> </div>
