</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>An asset is something of value that must be protected (e.g., a system, service, or data).</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Something of value that has to be protected, such as a system component or data.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-99" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">99</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_606"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:99_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=530993&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11550&amp;slot=99&amp;checksum=4636b5eda2d46c444ae7c74b069718e2&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
