<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:101_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:101_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:101_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>What is a <b>vulnerability</b> in a computer-based system?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 101</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:101_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:101_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:101_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:101_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A user account that has multi-factor authentication enabled.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:101_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:101_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:101_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:101_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A weakness that may be exploited to cause loss or harm.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:101_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:101_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:101_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:101_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A guarantee that data will remain correct under all conditions.</div></div> </div>
