<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:109_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:109_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:109_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:109_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because deterministic software is impossible to build in practice.</div></div> </div>
