<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:110_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:110_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:110_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:110_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">An attacker inserts a fake transaction into a banking system.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Interception threats allow an attacker to gain unauthorized access to an asset, such as reading confidential data in transit or at rest.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: An attacker captures network traffic to obtain confidential user data being transferred.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-111" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">111</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_678"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:111_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531005&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11554&amp;slot=111&amp;checksum=1831f983c4312be93b157fd26c6d7dfb&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:111_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:111_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:111_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Complex systems often address 'wicked problems'. What is a key implication for defining system success?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 111</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:111_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:111_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:111_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:111_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Success may be subjective and depend on stakeholder perspectives and real-world effectiveness after deployment, not just original specifications.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:111_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:111_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:111_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:111_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">If a contract is signed, the system is automatically successful.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:111_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:111_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:111_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:111_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Success can always be measured objectively by counting lines of code delivered.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:111_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:111_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:111_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:111_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Wicked problems imply that requirements can be completely specified up front with no ambiguity.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Stakeholders may disagree on goals and measures, so success is a judgment often assessed after deployment.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Success may be subjective and depend on stakeholder perspectives and real-world effectiveness after deployment, not just original specifications.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-112" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">112</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_684"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:112_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531006&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11573&amp;slot=112&amp;checksum=eca66143b6d12abd193ddd702d23bf6b&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:112_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:112_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:112_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Complex systems often address 'wicked problems'. What is a key implication for defining system success?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 112</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:112_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:112_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:112_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:112_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">If a contract is signed, the system is automatically successful.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:112_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:112_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:112_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:112_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Success can always be measured objectively by counting lines of code delivered.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:112_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:112_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:112_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:112_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Success may be subjective and depend on stakeholder perspectives and real-world effectiveness after deployment, not just original specifications.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:112_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:112_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:112_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:112_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Wicked problems imply that requirements can be completely specified up front with no ambiguity.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Stakeholders may disagree on goals and measures, so success is a judgment often assessed after deployment.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Success may be subjective and depend on stakeholder perspectives and real-world effectiveness after deployment, not just original specifications.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-113" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">113</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_690"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:113_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531007&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11487&amp;slot=113&amp;checksum=fd1d363583fb5e41b7a2b69958f1e935&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
