<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:113_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:113_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:113_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:113_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Overwhelming a web server with requests so legitimate users cannot connect.</div></div> </div>
