</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Modification threats involve tampering with assets, such as altering or destroying records.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: An attacker changes stored records so the information becomes incorrect or unreliable.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-117" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">117</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_714"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:117_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531011&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11556&amp;slot=117&amp;checksum=f467a9b44984757fab5da5fd6551a886&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
