<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:128_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:128_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:128_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>What is a primary purpose of an organizational <b>security policy</b>?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 128</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:128_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:128_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:128_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:128_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">To guarantee that no system will ever be attacked.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:128_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:128_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:128_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:128_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">To replace all technical design documents with a single long and highly detailed manual.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:128_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:128_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:128_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:128_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">To communicate broad security goals and expectations so security decisions are consistent and understandable across the organization.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:128_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:128_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:128_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:128_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">To ensure all assets receive the same highest level of protection.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Security policies set broad goals and strategies to guide security decisions and communicate expectations across the organization.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: To communicate broad security goals and expectations so security decisions are consistent and understandable across the organization.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-129" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">129</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_786"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:129_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531023&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11579&amp;slot=129&amp;checksum=361445a40613c900afd13e52b92473ad&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:129_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:129_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:129_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Large system development efforts often use a plan-driven approach. Which reason best explains this tendency?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 129</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:129_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:129_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:129_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:129_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because different parts (hardware, software, communications) are developed in parallel and hardware changes are expensive, limiting iteration between phases.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:129_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:129_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:129_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:129_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because agile methods cannot be used for any software project.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:129_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:129_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:129_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:129_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because testing is unnecessary when a plan exists.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:129_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:129_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:129_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:129_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because plan-driven approaches require no stakeholder input.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Parallel hardware/software/communications work and costly hardware changes reduce room for frequent iteration.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Because different parts (hardware, software, communications) are developed in parallel and hardware changes are expensive, limiting iteration between phases.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-130" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">130</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_792"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:130_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531024&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11493&amp;slot=130&amp;checksum=add55a9cf8618e6c0b6bfe8a310427dd&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:130_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:130_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:130_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which sequence best matches common stages of security risk assessment across a system's life?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 130</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:130_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:130_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:130_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:130_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Penetration testing → user training → hardware replacement.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:130_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:130_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:130_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:130_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Preliminary risk assessment → life cycle/design risk assessment → operational risk assessment.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:130_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:130_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:130_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:130_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Operational risk assessment → preliminary risk assessment → life cycle/design risk assessment.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:130_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:130_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:130_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:130_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Code compilation → UI testing → performance benchmarking.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>A typical view includes a preliminary assessment (early feasibility), assessment during the life cycle (design/implementation), and operational assessment (usage and human behavior after deployment).</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Preliminary risk assessment → life cycle/design risk assessment → operational risk assessment.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-131" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">131</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_798"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:131_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531025&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11560&amp;slot=131&amp;checksum=8ae5647fe19a1378ab4b2385d9ad70c3&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:131_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:131_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:131_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>In a system development process, what does <em>requirements partitioning</em> primarily involve?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 131</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:131_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:131_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:131_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:131_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Deciding which subsystems are responsible for implementing specific system requirements.</div></div> </div>
