<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:134_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:134_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:134_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Why can increased automation in system operation sometimes raise cost and reduce flexibility?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 134</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:134_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:134_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:134_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:134_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because automation eliminates the need for requirements engineering.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:134_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:134_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:134_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:134_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because automated systems always improve usability and never introduce complexity.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:134_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:134_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:134_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:134_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because humans cannot be trained to operate systems.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:134_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:134_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:134_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:134_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because automation requires designing for many anticipated failure modes and automated behavior is less adaptable than humans in unexpected situations.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Automation must handle anticipated failure modes and tends to be inflexible compared to adaptable human operators.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Because automation requires designing for many anticipated failure modes and automated behavior is less adaptable than humans in unexpected situations.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-135" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">135</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_822"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:135_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531029&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11581&amp;slot=135&amp;checksum=6398de78f37b3f2935e92f36d590fa8d&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:135_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:135_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:135_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Why can increased automation in system operation sometimes raise cost and reduce flexibility?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 135</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:135_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:135_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:135_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:135_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because humans cannot be trained to operate systems.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:135_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:135_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:135_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:135_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because automated systems always improve usability and never introduce complexity.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:135_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:135_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:135_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:135_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because automation eliminates the need for requirements engineering.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:135_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:135_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:135_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:135_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Because automation requires designing for many anticipated failure modes and automated behavior is less adaptable than humans in unexpected situations.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Automation must handle anticipated failure modes and tends to be inflexible compared to adaptable human operators.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Because automation requires designing for many anticipated failure modes and automated behavior is less adaptable than humans in unexpected situations.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-136" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">136</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_828"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:136_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531030&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11495&amp;slot=136&amp;checksum=b97742fbd18b6c1487baee868d9cc246&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:136_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:136_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:136_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>What is the primary goal of <b>penetration testing</b> in security validation?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 136</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:136_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:136_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:136_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:136_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">To attempt to breach system security by simulating realistic attacks and finding exploitable weaknesses.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:136_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:136_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:136_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:136_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">To increase system throughput by removing security checks.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:136_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:136_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:136_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:136_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">To replace the need for secure design by adding more servers.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:136_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:136_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:136_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:136_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">To prove mathematically that all security requirements are satisfied.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Penetration testing simulates attacks with the explicit aim of breaching security to discover vulnerabilities and weaknesses.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: To attempt to breach system security by simulating realistic attacks and finding exploitable weaknesses.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-137" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">137</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_834"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:137_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531031&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11510&amp;slot=137&amp;checksum=0ab7c3ceefa1309c8680b66a079d706f&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:137_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:137_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:137_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which statement best describes a <b>software product line</b>?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 137</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:137_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:137_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:137_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:137_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A set of related applications sharing a common architecture and components, specialized for different requirements.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:137_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:137_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:137_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:137_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A random collection of unrelated apps in an app store.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:137_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:137_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:137_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:137_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A single application that cannot be modified to avoid version fragmentation.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:137_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:137_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:137_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:137_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A system that only reuses design patterns and no actual components.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: A set of related applications sharing a common architecture and components, specialized for different requirements.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-138" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">138</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_840"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:138_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531032&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11496&amp;slot=138&amp;checksum=b84e32ac6968bdb7c52e967f7f91df7a&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:138_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:138_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:138_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which option best describes <b>system reuse</b> in software engineering?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 138</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:138_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:138_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:138_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:138_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Reusing only small utility functions such as string helpers.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:138_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:138_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:138_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:138_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Reusing a design idea without any actual software artifacts.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:138_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:138_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:138_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:138_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Reusing complete systems that may include several application programs.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:138_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:138_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:138_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:138_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Reusing a single class by copying its source code into a new project.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Reusing complete systems that may include several application programs.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-139" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">139</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_846"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:139_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531033&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11516&amp;slot=139&amp;checksum=50d848e515a6e915751ba7815f3a8069&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:139_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:139_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:139_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which statement best captures the essence of a software service in service-based systems?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 139</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:139_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:139_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:139_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:139_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">It always results in transferring ownership of underlying resources to the user.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:139_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:139_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:139_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:139_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">It must always be deployed together with its client application.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:139_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:139_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:139_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:139_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">It requires all consumers to use the same programming language and platform.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:139_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:139_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:139_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:139_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">It delivers functionality that is independent of the application using it.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>A key idea is that the service is provided independently of any single consuming application.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: It delivers functionality that is independent of the application using it.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-140" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">140</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_852"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:140_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531034&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11517&amp;slot=140&amp;checksum=3357070f1a9ed335042fd3c0258ef2eb&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:140_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:140_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:140_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Compared with traditional software components, which feature is most characteristic of services in service-based systems?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 140</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:140_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:140_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:140_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:140_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They must be linked at compile time into a single executable.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:140_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:140_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:140_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:140_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They require a graphical user interface for every operation.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:140_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:140_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:140_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:140_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They can only be accessed through shared-memory method calls.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:140_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:140_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:140_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:140_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They are independent and do not rely on a 'requires' interface.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Services are designed as independent units accessed via message-based communication.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: They are independent and do not rely on a 'requires' interface.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-141" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">141</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_858"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:141_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531035&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11518&amp;slot=141&amp;checksum=478689ccd7f94cbabae40c0ec8e01e7b&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:141_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:141_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:141_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>In a service-oriented approach, what does 'loosely coupled' most directly imply?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 141</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:141_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:141_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:141_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:141_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Consumers interact through standardized messages rather than internal implementation details.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:141_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:141_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:141_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:141_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Services must run on the same machine as the client.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:141_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:141_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:141_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:141_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">All services must share one database schema.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:141_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:141_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:141_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:141_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Interfaces are unnecessary because services are self-describing at runtime in all cases.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Loose coupling helps services evolve and be replaced without forcing changes in consumers beyond the interface contract.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Consumers interact through standardized messages rather than internal implementation details.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-142" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">142</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_864"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:142_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531036&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11519&amp;slot=142&amp;checksum=4b1bf99b43105cccb57c7ab12bd4f5f4&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:142_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:142_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:142_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>What is a key benefit of delaying the binding of services until deployment or execution?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 142</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:142_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:142_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:142_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:142_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">It eliminates the need for interface documentation.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:142_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:142_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:142_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:142_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">It guarantees that no network failures can occur.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:142_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:142_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:142_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:142_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">It forces all service providers to use the same internal design.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:142_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:142_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:142_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:142_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Applications can adapt to changes by selecting more appropriate services at runtime.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Late binding supports adaptation to changing environments and providers.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Applications can adapt to changes by selecting more appropriate services at runtime.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-143" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">143</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_870"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:143_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531037&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11520&amp;slot=143&amp;checksum=2fd84c98a13a5e22c2dac08c6486cc4c&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:143_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:143_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:143_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>In a typical service-oriented architecture, which set of roles is fundamental to how services are published and used?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 143</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:143_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:143_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:143_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:143_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Browser, DNS server, and certificate authority.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:143_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:143_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:143_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:143_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Database administrator, system operator, and end user.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:143_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:143_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:143_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:143_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Service provider, service requester, and a service registry.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:143_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:143_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:143_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:143_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Compiler, linker, and loader.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>A common pattern is provider publishes, requester finds, then binds using an agreed protocol.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Service provider, service requester, and a service registry.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-144" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">144</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_876"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:144_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531038&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11521&amp;slot=144&amp;checksum=02f851af599e69d3cf4f8ba890420c93&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
