</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>REST is an architectural style centered on resources and transferring their representations between clients and servers.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: An architectural style based on transferring representations of resources from server to client.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-147" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">147</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_894"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:147_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531041&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11524&amp;slot=147&amp;checksum=27a6cf0fce6785e5b08d6b6518110b44&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:147_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:147_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:147_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>In a RESTful architecture, what is a 'resource'?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 147</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:147_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:147_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:147_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:147_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Only a physical device connected to the network.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:147_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:147_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:147_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:147_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A single immutable file format that cannot change representation.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:147_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:147_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:147_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:147_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">A data element identified by a URL and representable in multiple formats (e.g., PDF, HTML).</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:147_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:147_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:147_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:147_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Only a server-side thread that handles a request.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>A resource is a data element (e.g., record, catalog, document) that can be represented in different formats.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: A data element identified by a URL and representable in multiple formats (e.g., PDF, HTML).</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-148" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">148</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_900"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:148_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531042&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11525&amp;slot=148&amp;checksum=67fdaeaff07b46ec5ec688f56de7e107&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:148_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:148_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:148_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which mapping between CRUD-style operations and HTTP verbs is most commonly associated with RESTful services?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 148</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:148_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:148_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:148_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:148_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Create→PUT, Read→DELETE, Update→GET, Delete→POST.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:148_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:148_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:148_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:148_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">CRUD does not map to HTTP verbs in RESTful designs.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:148_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:148_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:148_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:148_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Create→POST, Read→GET, Update→PUT, Delete→DELETE.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:148_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:148_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:148_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:148_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Create→GET, Read→POST, Update→DELETE, Delete→PUT.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>A typical mapping is Create→POST, Read→GET, Update→PUT, Delete→DELETE.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Create→POST, Read→GET, Update→PUT, Delete→DELETE.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-149" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">149</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_906"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:149_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531043&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11526&amp;slot=149&amp;checksum=5da765c582a7d9730f257fcc8f293475&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:149_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:149_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:149_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>A RESTful service exposes a collection of resources at a base URL. Which approach is most appropriate for requesting a specific date's data without changing the resource identity?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 149</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:149_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:149_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:149_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:149_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Use a URL query parameter such as <span>...?date=20250115</span> with GET.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:149_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:149_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:149_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:149_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Use DELETE to indicate the date to retrieve.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:149_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:149_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:149_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:149_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Encode the date in a client-side file name and upload it.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:149_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:149_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:149_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:149_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Send the date only by emailing the service provider.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Query parameters are commonly used to refine a request (e.g., filtering by date).</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Use a URL query parameter such as <span>...?date=20250115</span> with GET.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-150" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">150</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_912"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:150_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531044&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11527&amp;slot=150&amp;checksum=cd9ef4a1750c389310d83e1db300eefb&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:150_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:150_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:150_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which is a commonly cited disadvantage of using RESTful services compared with more formalized 'big web service' stacks?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 150</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:150_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:150_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:150_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:150_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">REST cannot use HTTP or HTTPS as transport protocols.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:150_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:150_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:150_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:150_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">REST forces all services to be stateful and session-based.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:150_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:150_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:150_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:150_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">REST cannot represent documents or records as resources.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:150_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:150_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:150_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:150_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">There is no single standardized way to describe RESTful interfaces, so users may rely on informal documentation.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>REST does not mandate standard interface description and often requires custom approaches to QoS monitoring/management.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: There is no single standardized way to describe RESTful interfaces, so users may rely on informal documentation.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-151" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">151</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_918"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:151_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531045&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11528&amp;slot=151&amp;checksum=e72560f728afd6fbf177f99d4ed96572&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:151_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:151_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:151_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Service engineering is primarily concerned with:</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 151</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:151_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:151_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:151_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:151_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Developing dependable, reusable services intended for use across different systems.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:151_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:151_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:151_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:151_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Replacing all network protocols with proprietary ones to reduce interoperability.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:151_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:151_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:151_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:151_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Eliminating the need for testing by using only third-party services.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:151_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:151_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:151_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:151_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Optimizing a single application's user interface for one device type.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>It focuses on developing robust, reusable services and documenting them for discovery and use.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Developing dependable, reusable services intended for use across different systems.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-152" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">152</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_924"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:152_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531046&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11529&amp;slot=152&amp;checksum=b629e3d25c615ffab3a44f92525b5bba&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:152_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:152_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:152_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which sequence best matches typical stages in a service engineering process?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 152</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:152_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:152_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:152_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:152_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Code obfuscation → UI prototyping → branding review.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:152_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:152_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:152_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:152_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Testing only → deployment only → documentation only.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:152_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:152_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:152_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:152_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Database migration → hardware procurement → office rollout.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:152_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:152_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:152_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:152_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Service candidate identification → service design → service implementation and deployment.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>A common sequence is candidate identification, design, then implementation and deployment.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Service candidate identification → service design → service implementation and deployment.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-153" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">153</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_930"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:153_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531047&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11530&amp;slot=153&amp;checksum=b9c47fc4354518f90d40451d57e1471c&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:153_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:153_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:153_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which classification correctly distinguishes three fundamental types of services used in service-based systems?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 153</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:153_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:153_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:153_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:153_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Compile-time services, link-time services, and run-time services.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:153_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:153_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:153_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:153_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Monolithic services, spaghetti services, and untyped services.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:153_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:153_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:153_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:153_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Kernel services, driver services, and firmware services.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:153_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:153_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:153_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:153_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Utility services, business services, and coordination services.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Utility services provide general-purpose functions, business services implement business functions, and coordination services support composite processes.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Utility services, business services, and coordination services.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-154" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">154</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_936"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:154_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531048&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11531&amp;slot=154&amp;checksum=8640520689aab0567345b8e446c87c89&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:154_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:154_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:154_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which statement best describes task-oriented vs entity-oriented services?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 154</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:154_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:154_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:154_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:154_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Task-oriented services must always be implemented with SOAP, not REST.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:154_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:154_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:154_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:154_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Task-oriented services store only images, while entity-oriented services store only numbers.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:154_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:154_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:154_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:154_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Entity-oriented services cannot be reused across business processes.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:154_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:154_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:154_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:154_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Task-oriented services focus on activities, while entity-oriented services focus on business entities such as forms or records.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Task-oriented services align with activities, while entity-oriented services align with business entities (similar to objects).</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Task-oriented services focus on activities, while entity-oriented services focus on business entities such as forms or records.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-155" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">155</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_942"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:155_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531049&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11532&amp;slot=155&amp;checksum=c0f605c54e1833125a3d854586e340ec&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:155_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:155_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:155_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which statement is most accurate about coordination services in service-based systems?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 155</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:155_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:155_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:155_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:155_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They only provide general-purpose utilities such as currency conversion.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:155_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:155_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:155_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:155_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They support composite business processes and are always task-oriented.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:155_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:155_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:155_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:155_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They cannot be implemented using workflows.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:155_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:155_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:155_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:155_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They are always entity-oriented and never include control flow.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Coordination services support composite processes and are typically task-oriented.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: They support composite business processes and are always task-oriented.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-156" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">156</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_948"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:156_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531050&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11533&amp;slot=156&amp;checksum=c7123c92777ac7df5d1bb93411eeb4be&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:156_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:156_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:156_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>When identifying potential services, which question is most directly about service independence and external reuse?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 156</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:156_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:156_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:156_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:156_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Does the service require a specific brand of keyboard?</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:156_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:156_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:156_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:156_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Could the service be used by clients outside the organisation?</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:156_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:156_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:156_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:156_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Should the logo be redesigned before deployment?</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:156_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:156_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:156_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:156_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Will all users always have identical non-functional requirements?</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Service identification often considers independence and whether clients outside the organization could use the service.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Could the service be used by clients outside the organisation?</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-157" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">157</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_954"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:157_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531051&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11534&amp;slot=157&amp;checksum=55600c1ff6acd989bfb8a181a8b72189&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:157_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:157_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:157_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Which design principle best aligns with efficient service interface design?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 157</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:157_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:157_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:157_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:157_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Maximize the number of round trips so that each field is confirmed separately.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:157_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:157_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:157_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:157_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Hide all errors by returning success for every request.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:157_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:157_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:157_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:157_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Use different message formats for every consumer to avoid standardization.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:157_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:157_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:157_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:157_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">Minimize the number of messages needed to complete a service request.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Service interfaces should usually minimize the number of messages exchanged to complete a request.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: Minimize the number of messages needed to complete a service request.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-158" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">158</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_960"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:158_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531052&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11535&amp;slot=158&amp;checksum=e86a21240519e20697a6fa19087f1aea&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
