<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:159_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:159_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:159_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>Why do many organizations choose RESTful services over more 'heavyweight' web-service stacks in some cases?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 159</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:159_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:159_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:159_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:159_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They require no URLs because resources are addressed by memory pointer.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:159_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:159_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:159_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:159_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They completely eliminate the need for any transport protocol.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:159_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:159_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:159_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:159_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They guarantee perfect reliability without monitoring or management.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:159_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:159_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:159_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:159_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">They tend to be simpler and impose lower overhead for many web-based scenarios.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>RESTful services often have lower overhead and simpler implementation using standard web mechanisms.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: They tend to be simpler and impose lower overhead for many web-based scenarios.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-160" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">160</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_972"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:160_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531054&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11537&amp;slot=160&amp;checksum=bd7ed44340e3a6c5497d37baad7976c3&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
<input type="hidden" class="questionflagvalue" id="q21665:160_:flaggedcheckbox" name="q21665:160_:flagged" value="0"><a tabindex="0" class="aabtn" role="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="İşaretli" title="İlerisi için bu soruyu işaretle"><img class="questionflagimage" src="https://online-learning2025-2026.gidatarim.edu.tr/theme/image.php/academi/core/1762167339/i/unflagged" alt="">Soruyu işaretle</a></div></div><div class="content"><div class="formulation clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Soru metini</h4><input type="hidden" name="q21665:160_:sequencecheck" value="2"><div class="qtext"><div class="clearfix"><p>How can service-based systems help preserve investment in existing (legacy) systems?</p></div></div><fieldset class="ablock no-overflow visual-scroll-x"><legend class="prompt h6 fw-normal "><span class="visually-hidden">Soru 160</span> Lütfen birini seçin:</legend><div class="answer"><div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:160_answer" disabled="disabled" value="0" id="q21665:160_answer0" aria-labelledby="q21665:160_answer0_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:160_answer0_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">a. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">By preventing any external applications from accessing legacy functions.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:160_answer" disabled="disabled" value="1" id="q21665:160_answer1" aria-labelledby="q21665:160_answer1_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:160_answer1_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">b. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">By deleting legacy systems and rewriting everything from scratch.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q21665:160_answer" disabled="disabled" value="2" id="q21665:160_answer2" aria-labelledby="q21665:160_answer2_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:160_answer2_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">c. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">By forcing legacy code to be converted into a mobile app UI.</div></div> </div>
<div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q21665:160_answer" disabled="disabled" value="3" id="q21665:160_answer3" aria-labelledby="q21665:160_answer3_label"><div class="d-flex w-auto" id="q21665:160_answer3_label" data-region="answer-label"><span class="answernumber">d. </span><div class="flex-fill ms-1">By implementing service interfaces that provide access to legacy functionality.</div></div> </div>
</div></fieldset></div><div class="outcome clearfix"><h4 class="accesshide">Geri bildirim</h4><div class="feedback"><div class="generalfeedback"><div class="clearfix"><p>Legacy functionality can be exposed through service interfaces so external applications can reuse it.</p></div></div><div class="rightanswer">Doğru cevap: By implementing service interfaces that provide access to legacy functionality.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="question-21665-161" class="que multichoice interactive notanswered"><div class="info"><h3 class="no">Soru <span class="qno">161</span></h3><div class="state">Cevaplanmadı</div><div class="grade">1,00 üzerinden puanlanmış</div><div class="questionflag editable" id="yui_3_18_1_1_1767644350614_978"><input type="hidden" name="q21665:161_:flagged" value="0"><input type="hidden" value="qaid=531055&amp;qubaid=21665&amp;qid=11538&amp;slot=161&amp;checksum=772406be48114f9abd68a2433db3180a&amp;sesskey=bsAI63OWde&amp;newstate=" class="questionflagpostdata">
